nx.description: The binary has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

pie.description: The shared object is build with -fPIC flag which enables Position independent code. This makes Return Oriented Programming (ROP) attacks much more difficult to execute reliably.

stack_canary.description: This binary has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

runpath.description: The binary does not have RUNPATH set.

playstore_details.title: Lose Weight - Weight Loss App
playstore_details.description:
🏆 The best choice for healthy and rapid weight loss, helping you lose weight in just 30 days! It’s expertly designed to support your weight loss journey with systematic workouts and diet plans at your disposal. Focused on safe and sustainable results, you’ll lose stubborn fat, lose inches off your waistline, lose excess pounds, and improve your health and fitness.

The weight loss plan contains arm, butt, abdominal, and leg workouts aimed at helping you lose weight and shaping your body. With animations and video guidance, you can ensure that you use the right form during every exercise, optimizing your efforts for weight loss. No equipment is needed, making it easy to lose weight at home or anywhere, anytime.

📣 Best Weight Loss App 
Looking for fitness apps? Hard to lose weight? Not satisfied with weight loss apps? Try our “Lose Weight in 30 Days” for safe and fast weight loss! This fitness app free for women provides effective workouts and diet plans. It's one of the best weight loss apps available!

⭐ Features ⭐
√ Track your calories and weight changes.
√ Low calorie diet plans
√ 3 workout intensity options
√ Animations and video guidance
√ Sustainable training plans for all body areas
√ Lose weight with a professional coach
√ Quick and Powerful Workouts
√ Customize your training plan
√ Set your workout reminders
√ Share with your friends on social media 

🥦 30-Day Healthy Eating Plan
We provide daily low-calorie meal plans to support your weight loss. Enjoy perfect recipes for every meal, from breakfast to dinner and snacks. Achieve your goals with a balanced diet that helps you stay on track and lose weight effectively.

🔥 3 intensity levels to choose from
Never worry about keeping up! You can choose from three training intensity levels: beginner, intermediate, and advanced. Pick the one that suits your fitness level and enjoy your workout.

🗓️ Customize your training plan
Create a workout plan tailored to your unique needs! By integrating details such as your BMI, exercise habits, fitness goals, we craft a customized training program that maximizes your weight loss results and keeps you motivated.

🏠 Workout at Home 
Enjoy the benefits of home workouts with no equipment needed! Lose weight and stay fit with exercises that use just your body weight. This makes it easy to achieve your fitness goals anytime, anywhere.

🏃‍♀️ Fitness Coach
All sport & workouts are designed by professional fitness coach. These guides will help you through your weight loss journey, just like having a personal fitness coach in your pocket!

💪 Burning Workouts & HIIT Workouts
Burn calories and lose weight fast with high-intensity workouts. Our HIIT sessions are designed to maximize calorie burn and accelerate weight loss. Push your limits to shed pounds quickly and effectively with intense training.

📈 Track your workout
You can track your weight loss progress with detailed graphs and accurately count your calories. The data can be synchronized on Google Fit, allowing you to monitor your achievements seamlessly across devices and stay motivated on your weight loss journey.
